social_posts.post_text:
Almost Valentine’s Day! ♥️ have you asked anyone? Have you been asked?? 

Photo by @lightingafterdark

Want to share some of my own art on here more often 😁 I’ll do monthly updates! Here’s some art I’ve created in the past month♥️ always trying to keep going forward with practice! I have no doubts that art is what I want to spend my whole life doing and creating💖 I may not be the greatest , but I’m determined! 🔥 
#art

Yesterday I went and got my first ever tattoo! 🥲♥️ I thought for years about what I wanted, and at some point I just have to admit my full obsession with Avatar the Last Airbender… 🤣 First naming my cat MoMo, and second getting Tui and La 🥹 I gave @sweetbaphomet the simplest reference and she completely made it her own style, I was in love the moment I saw it! I knew she was the right person to go too no doubt! Thanks again Steph ♥️ And big thanks to @lanbui for spending the whole day with me and documenting the experience, and being a bestie ! The best day 💖 and lol at my face in the last one 🤣🤣

Today I turn 25 🥲 technically in a few minutes from posting this! Birthdays always make you think about your life, and I’m so so happy to say that I’m proud of all I did while being 24! The amount of knowledge , growth and confidence I’ve gained this year I would trade for nothing. I’m grateful everyday for being given opportunities to do what I love, so thank you universe and everyone apart of my life. You make me complete 🙂♥️

Attended my first @renaissancepleasurefaire today! It was just so fun to dress up and be teleported to a different world for a while. Everyone was so kind and the stores and art were all so unique. Definitely going to continue going through the years 🏰 I got myself a flower crown I’ll keep forever ! 🌼🌼🌼

Back in 2019 while working at @barnyardfx, we got the opportunity to work on a model for The Little Mermaid! It was a really great experience, seeing inside one warehouse/office full of marine inspiration everywhere. You walked in and were taken to an underwater reference wonderland !🤣 I was really thankful to have a lot of trust put in me by @gregaronowitz , he showed me what to do but then let me have time to do it on my own. And having creative freedom with the plants was such a fun part! Although spray painting every side of every flower was very time consuming, it did make for a good effect being all one color 😊 which was requested so that it could be scanned digitally easier. I hope to catch a glimpse of this shape with the sisters, which was where it was intended to be. The concept art is the second slide, so beautiful 😊♥️ forever grateful to have had the tiniest part in something special. Even if you don’t like the movie, hopefully you can appreciate the art behind it ☺️
And sorry I look so greasy in the pic 🤣🤣🤣 it’s all I got

Last spring to be apart of the crew at @theonyxforgeofficial was a dream come true! Worked on several things but it’s the combination of everyone’s abilities that make it come together so nicely in the end. This costume was for @waltongogginsbonafide for the show by @bootsriley “I’m a Virgo” ! It’s a powerful show ♥️ 
Thank you again to @stevewangcreaturecreator and @whatisacleve for allowing me to help out ! 🥰

#imavirgo #art

This year I got to help out on a booth at Anime Expo for BiliBili 😄 My main focus was the tv mascot! @gregaronowitz built the body of the character, and cut out the first technical side of the face. I used his parts to cut a second copy of each. There was a satisfying 100 pieces! 🥰 I tried to lay things down as accurately to the art then glued down when they were in position, it was so nice to finally see it coming together! The hardest part was painting in between the spaces. It took 4 coats to make it look nice 😂 took about 6 hours per side! @megan_art was an absolute joy to work with, so funny, we’ve been working together in the same shop for nearly a year, but this was the first time we worked side by side! We’re both usually doing our own thing so it was nice to blend with you! She helped with so much of the body shopping and the painting ☺️ another fun project completed! ♥️ on to the next! 

#art #animeexpo #bilibili

Happy to be able to have helped make this “lil” guy with @barnyardfx for @alexpardee ! 
Molding , Casting, and lots of sanding was my part! Wish I took a couple more photos from in progress. 
Sculpted and painted by @gregaronowitz 😊👍 
Hope you get a chance to see this dude in person at Alex’s comic con booth!! 
#brightmares #art

Never made an official post about this job, so thought spooky season would be the best! Throwback to helping out @stevewangcreaturecreator with his monsterpalooza creations! I was really honored to be able to have a hand helping in these pieces. The work I did was mainly on making two of these Spider Reapers! I casted the body, (and yes I was rolling on the floor with this mold🤣) casted his teeth, and body shopped his seam! Also in the mean time was casting Steve’s smaller busts of iconic characters 🥰♥️ I learned such an incredible amount this job from @whatisacleve and will always be thankful for my time spent there 😁 also slush casted that base but I can’t remember who it went too 🤣🤣
#art #sculpture #monsterpalooza
